              "type": "setWorldFlag",
              "flag": "anomaly_hoarded",
              "value": true
            },
            {
              "type": "log",
              "text": "{self.name} ordered the find catalogued, crated, and kept — not sold, not studied, just held, the way wise houses hold things they do not yet understand. There is a patience that looks like greed and a greed that looks like patience. Only time tells which this was."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "study_it",
          "requires": [
